claim.claim-text:
1. An instrument for detecting radiation from a surface of a biosensor having a surface grating structure, wherein a sample to be tested is placed on the surface grating structure, comprising:
a broadband light source;
an optical system directing collimated light from the broadband light source to the surface of the biosensor so as to illuminate the surface;
apparatus detecting radiation from the biosensor in response to the illumination from the optical system, and
a processing unit coupled to the detection apparatus programmed to derive a peak wavelength value of the detected radiation.
